But no one line is an island unto itself. Single speccing is a known way to gimp yourself. You will have MORE control, but less DD and DOT ability. This is by design and I don't think it is bad.<P>Let us not forget, you still have baseline DOT and Drain, no matter how you spec. This is one argument that will fall on it's face unfortunately.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...
